{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01GqrdmKz3tcnenBULg9iRwg","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## Summary\n\nHere's what I found about the backend package structure:\n\n### **Dependencies Available**\n\n**Production:**\n- `hono@^4.6.0` — Lightweight web framework (handles routing and middleware)\n- `postgres@^3.4.0` — Native PostgreSQL client\n- `@solana/web3.js@^1.98.0` — Solana blockchain library\n\n**Dev:**\n- `@rng-utopia/config` — Shared config package (workspace reference)\n- `tsx@^4.7.0` — TypeScript executor for Node\n- `typescript@^5.7.0`\n- `vitest@^2.1.0` — Test framework\n\n### **TypeScript/ESM Setup**\n\n- **Type**: `\"module\"` in package.json — pure ESM (no CommonJS)\n- **tsconfig extends**: `@rng-utopia/config/tsconfig.node.json` (shared config)\n- **Root**: `src/`\n- **Output**: `dist/`\n- **Node types**: Included\n\n### **Import Patterns Used**\n\n1. **Named imports with explicit `.js` extensions** (ESM compliance):\n   ```ts\n   import { loadConfig } from \"./config.js\";\n   ```\n\n2. **Named imports for dependencies**:\n   ```ts\n   import { Keypair } from \"@solana/web3.js\";\n   import { Hono } from \"hono\";\n   ```\n\n3. **Default export** from index.ts for Hono app (for edge runtime compatibility):\n   ```ts\n   export default {\n     port,\n     fetch: app.fetch,\n   };\n   ```\n\n### **Config Module Structure** (`src/config.ts`)\n\n**Exports:**\n- `interface Config` — Type definition with:\n  - `port: number`\n  - `databaseUrl: string`\n  - `rpcUrl: string`\n  - `serverKeypair: Keypair`\n\n- `function loadConfig(): Config` — Loads environment variables:\n  - `PORT` (optional, defaults to 3100)\n  - `DATABASE_URL` (required)\n  - `RPC_URL` (required)\n  - `SERVER_KEYPAIR` (required) — Parsed as JSON array of secret key bytes\n\n**Helpers:**\n- `requireEnv(name)` — Throws if env var missing\n- `parseKeypair(raw)` — Converts JSON array to Keypair with error handling\n\n### **Index Entry Point** (`src/index.ts`)\n\n- Loads config first\n- Creates Hono app instance\n- Single `/health` endpoint returning `{ status: \"ok\", version: \"0.1.0\" }`\n- Exports Hono app in object with `port` and `fetch` (for deployment to edge runtime/Cloudflare)\n- Comment indicates fairness routes will be wired in later\n\n**Key files:**\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/services/backend/package.json`\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/services/backend/tsconfig.json`\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/services/backend/src/config.ts`\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/services/backend/src/index.ts`"},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: ac3e77036943ce705 (for resuming to continue this agent's work if needed)\n<usage>total_tokens: 33522\ntool_uses: 4\nduration_ms: 10560</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"f4316b62-2257-4469-b202-66365945525c","uuid":"ba03e041-69d9-49ef-b2c7-ce0971f4c029","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"Read the following files to understand the backend package structure:\n1. `sources/rng-utopia/services/backend/package.json`\n2. `sources/rng-utopia/services/backend/tsconfig.json`\n3. `sources/rng-utopia/services/backend/src/config.ts`\n4. `sources/rng-utopia/services/backend/src/index.ts`\n\nI need to understand:\n- What dependencies are available\n- The TypeScript/ESM setup\n- Import patterns being used\n- The config module structure","agentId":"ac3e77036943ce705","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## Summary\n\nHere's what I found about the backend package structure:\n\n### **Dependencies Available**\n\n**Production:**\n- `hono@^4.6.0` — Lightweight web framework (handles routing and middleware)\n- `postgres@^3.4.0` — Native PostgreSQL client\n- `@solana/web3.js@^1.98.0` — Solana blockchain library\n\n**Dev:**\n- `@rng-utopia/config` — Shared config package (workspace reference)\n- `tsx@^4.7.0` — TypeScript executor for Node\n- `typescript@^5.7.0`\n- `vitest@^2.1.0` — Test framework\n\n### **TypeScript/ESM Setup**\n\n- **Type**: `\"module\"` in package.json — pure ESM (no CommonJS)\n- **tsconfig extends**: `@rng-utopia/config/tsconfig.node.json` (shared config)\n- **Root**: `src/`\n- **Output**: `dist/`\n- **Node types**: Included\n\n### **Import Patterns Used**\n\n1. **Named imports with explicit `.js` extensions** (ESM compliance):\n   ```ts\n   import { loadConfig } from \"./config.js\";\n   ```\n\n2. **Named imports for dependencies**:\n   ```ts\n   import { Keypair } from \"@solana/web3.js\";\n   import { Hono } from \"hono\";\n   ```\n\n3. **Default export** from index.ts for Hono app (for edge runtime compatibility):\n   ```ts\n   export default {\n     port,\n     fetch: app.fetch,\n   };\n   ```\n\n### **Config Module Structure** (`src/config.ts`)\n\n**Exports:**\n- `interface Config` — Type definition with:\n  - `port: number`\n  - `databaseUrl: string`\n  - `rpcUrl: string`\n  - `serverKeypair: Keypair`\n\n- `function loadConfig(): Config` — Loads environment variables:\n  - `PORT` (optional, defaults to 3100)\n  - `DATABASE_URL` (required)\n  - `RPC_URL` (required)\n  - `SERVER_KEYPAIR` (required) — Parsed as JSON array of secret key bytes\n\n**Helpers:**\n- `requireEnv(name)` — Throws if env var missing\n- `parseKeypair(raw)` — Converts JSON array to Keypair with error handling\n\n### **Index Entry Point** (`src/index.ts`)\n\n- Loads config first\n- Creates Hono app instance\n- Single `/health` endpoint returning `{ status: \"ok\", version: \"0.1.0\" }`\n- Exports Hono app in object with `port` and `fetch` (for deployment to edge runtime/Cloudflare)\n- Comment indicates fairness routes will be wired in later\n\n**Key files:**\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/services/backend/package.json`\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/services/backend/tsconfig.json`\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/services/backend/src/config.ts`\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/services/backend/src/index.ts`"}],"totalDurationMs":10560,"totalTokens":33522,"totalToolUseCount":4,"usage":{"input_tokens":7,"cache_creation_input_tokens":3637,"cache_read_input_tokens":29069,"output_tokens":809,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":3637},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}}}
